data.description: Looking for a dreamy country retreat?  Look no further.  This listing presents a remarkable opportunity to own a fantastic 5-acre lot with a charming all-brick ranch home + a spacious outbuilding surrounded by tranquility and beauty.  Newly painted walls, hardwood floors, stone fireplace, HUGE basement with a second kitchen!!!  This home has three bedrooms on the main level PLUS one true bedroom in the basement with two BONUS bedrooms (SIX total bedrooms if you aren't factoring in bedroom windows)!!  Concrete exterior patios both from the main level + basement are created for entertaining.  Your five acre plot consists of gently rolling land that is so beautiful - with walnut trees and other varieties sprinkled across the property.  There are two full concrete storm/safe rooms in the basement.  The laundry is on the main floor but there are additional hookups in the basement.  The outbuilding has two garage stalls (with lifts) as well as other rooms and even a half bathroom - electrical ran throughout in excess (220-volt outlet as well!) PLUS an RV dump station outside.  Check this out before it's gone!
